<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>长相让人吃惊</span></strong></span></p>
<p><img width="500" src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200824/6b46ec987a69400999c9385eeab0bfb8.jpeg" /></p>
